articles.title: Cyclone Ilsa sets a new wind record as it smashes into Australia's western coast - CNN
articles.description: Cyclone Ilsa smashed into a remote stretch of coast in Western Australia around midnight Thursday local time with wind speeds that broke previous records set more than 10 years ago in the same place.
